Summary: Orbs in the sky moving around and hovering over mountain range then shooting off in the sky.
divs: Sighting Detailsmy mom called me in the room.She said to look out the window and asked me what the orbs were.I said I did not know and called my fiance in and we watched them almost like "dance" around in the sky and hover over the mountain range behind my house then after almost 10 minutes the shot off into the sky and disappeared.
